The lifetime economic burden of keratoconus: a decision analysis using a markov 
model.

Rebenitsch RL(1), Kymes SM, Walline JJ, Gordon MO.

Author information:
(1)Department of Ophthalmology and Visual Sciences, Washington University School 
of Medicine, St. Louis, MO 63110-1093, USA.

PURPOSE: To estimate the expected incremental lifetime cost of treatment of 
keratoconus compared to the expected cost of the treatment of myopia.
DESIGN: Cost estimate from the patient's perspective using a Markov decision 
model.
